Step 1 : Create Github Account and signin

Step 2 : Create a Github repositry

Step 3 : Start Eclipse

Step 4 : Goto Search on Eclipse Search bar Git Repositry and click ok

Step 5 : Create a project on Eclipse (maven or java)

Step 6 : Do a right click on a project > Team > Add to git repositry

Step 7 : Again goto > Team > commit > drag to stage change > commit and push to the repositry


